# Path-based exclusions for scripts/check-secrets.sh content scans.
# Keep this list minimal and specific; do not add broad globs.
#
# Rationale for each allowlisted file:
# - Gemfile.lock / yarn.lock / ios/Podfile.lock: dependency lockfiles can contain high-entropy hashes
#   and token-like strings generated by package registries; these are reviewed build artifacts.
# - android/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar: vetted upstream Gradle wrapper binary tracked for
#   reproducible Android builds; contents can trigger false positives in binary scans.
Gemfile.lock
yarn.lock
ios/Podfile.lock
android/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar
